October 25, 2015 Live updates: Miami Dolphins vs. Houston Texans 
The Miami Dolphins take on the Houston Texans at Sun Life Stadium at 1 p.m. on Sunday, Oct. 25 
Miami Herald sportswriters Armando Salguero and Adam Beasley provide live updates Miami Dolphins fans celebrate as they defeat the Tennessee Titans at Nissan Stadium in Nashville, Tenn, October 18, 2015. CHARLES TRAINOR JR ctrainor@miamiherald.com i
